snippet.title: TrickShot Gameplay - Q1 2024
snippet.description: TrickShot is a neon-drenched, gravity-defying future sport where players are armed with style. As contestants in an electrified quest for glory, players will skate, shoot, and soar to the apex of skill and showmanship while riding sleek hover skates or hoverboards. Fusing the finesse of skating with the thrill of tactical gunplay. Players artfully chain together tricks and combat maneuvers as they face off in visually stunning skate park arenas. The elegant interplay of mobility and marksmanship creates a kinetic dance never before seen in a Multiplayer shooter.
